summary: I previously had  zero interest in James Charles (didn't know much about him tbh)  and didn't even know the existence of Tati...
body: I previously had zero interest in James Charles (didn’t know much about him tbh) and didn’t even know the existence of Tati but I straight up watched the entire 43 minute video of Tati shutting it down with class. What a woman. I’m subscribed to her now. A woman that mature and sincere and unapologetic about what she does deserves. We need more youtubers who actually care about being role models and about their fans beyond what goes into their pockets. Also seeing the live count of Tati gaining followers as James loses is so satisfying 💀

summary: Youtubers I actually love a lot.
body:
Youtubers I actually love a lot.

In light of recent events with a certain nude sending, cheating on wife bastard named projared, I’m going to reccomend you guys some really good Youtubers I’ve watched for a while and I think they are severely underrated! First up is a duo pair named UltraDirectorJester and TheNiskelLP. These 2 are let’s players of many games and are genuinely hilarious, one of my favorite lets plays of their’s is their L.A. Noire, their comedy is absolutely hysterical and I hope they get more attention! Next is a YouTuber named Senpai Blade who is doing let’s plays of Persona 5 and Xenoblade chronicles 2 as of now, what I like about him is his analysis of many things in the games he plays and his theorist side is very entertaining to see. I hope you all check them out sometime as they are not very well known as of now but I hope they get more popular in the future!
